onto baking tray.","Choux pastries can be filled with whipped cream or pastry cream and served with fresh fruit, dusted with icing sugar.","Fill choux pastries with cream cheese and fresh herbs for a savoury option.","Adjust the size and shape of the choux pastries to suit your taste and requirements."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","2h","18 pieces"]}